      "message": "Patch Set 4: Verified\n\nLustre b2_1 build: http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/14799/\n Lustre master build: http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master/1399/\n Distro/Arch: RHEL6.3/x86_64\n\n Clean upgrade and downgrade path: b2_1->master->b2_1\n\n Test steps:\n 1)  format and setup Lustre b2_1 filesystem\n 2)  extract a kernel tarball into a Lustre test directory\n 3)  shutdown the entire Lustre filesystem\n 4)  upgrade all Lustre servers and clients at once to Lustre master\n 5)  start the entire Lustre filesystem\n 6)  extract the same kernel tarball into a new Lustre test directory\n 7)  compare the old and new test directories (no difference)\n 8)  run auster test suite (iorssf, iorfpp, simul in parallel-scale.sh)\n 9)  shutdown the entire Lustre filesystem\n 10) downgrade all Lustre servers and clients at once to Lustre b2_1\n 11) start the entire Lustre filesystem\n 12) extract the same kernel tarball into another new Lustre test directory\n 13) compare the old and new test directories (no difference)\n 14) run auster test suite (iorssf, iorfpp, simul in parallel-scale.sh)\n 15) shutdown the entire Lustre filesystem\n\n The test passed. I'm uploading the test results to Maloo.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "95209d6a1350ef1a9f862bbd46e849cf253548ef",
